contentrichtext.text: '''Doctor Strange''' or '''Dr. Strange''' may refer to: *'''[[Doctor Strange]]''' (real name Stephen Strange) is a Marvel Comics superhero. **[[Doctor Strange (Spider-Man)]], the third season premiere of the Spider-Man animated series **[[Dr. Strange (1978 film)|''Dr. Strange'' (1978 film)]], a made-for-TV movie based on the Marvel Comics fictional character **''[[Doctor Strange: The Sorcerer Supreme]]'', a 2007 animated film *[[Doc Strange]], a Nedor Comics character named Doctor Thomas Hugo Strange *[[Hugo Strange]], a DC Comics character and recurring Batman villain *[[Dr. Strange Records]], a record label and record store located in Alta Loma, California *''[[Dr. Strangelove]]'', a 1964 film directed by Stanley Kubrick *[[Dr. Strangely Strange]], an experimental Irish folk group, formed in Dublin in 1967 {{disambig}}
